high_descs: Turn left walk straight then head to the  end of the table
Pick up the fork on the table
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the fork in the mug at the sink
Pick up the mug with fork in the sink
Turn around to your right facing the stove
Put the mug with fork on the left side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with fork on the counter

high_descs: Turn around, go past the green table on the right, turn around to face the fork on the table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Bring the fork to the sink on the right.
Put the fork in the mug in the sink.
Pick up the mug in the sink with the fork in it.
Turn around 270 degrees to face the stove.
Put the mug with fork on the counter, right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the table
Pick up the fork by the wine bottle from the table
Turn right and go to the sink on the right
Put the fork in the mug in the sink
Pick up the fork and mug from the sink
Turn around and face the stove
Place the mug and fork on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a fork and mug on a counter
